02:07:54.118 --> 02:07:55.718
With Madhuri Dixit.

02:07:56.345 --> 02:08:00.065
Why? - Because
she dances very nicely.

02:08:01.278 --> 02:08:04.426
Shut up.
Teacher's heart is thumping today.

02:08:04.619 --> 02:08:08.299
Tomorrow is teacher's wonderful day,
